      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Keep it Busy",
        "Client": "Bahari the Scientist",
        "Description": "Ugh! As if I didn\u0027t have enough\r\npaperwork as it is, and now\r\nI have to write down what I just\r\ngot finished talking to you about...\r\nTalk about inefficient! Anyway,\r\nyou know the deal: You hunt the\r\nmonster, I procure the Qurio!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Aurora Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Appel de l\u0027Oc\u00E9an glac\u00E9",
        "Client": "Bahari le scientifique",
        "Description": "Devoir \u00E9crire \u00E7a alors que je\r\nviens de te le dire, quel ennui !\r\nBref. J\u0027aimerais que tu chasses\r\nune Somnacanth aurore. Je la\r\ncapture, toi tu me prot\u00E8ges,\r\nc\u0027est tout. Pig\u00E9 ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Somnacanth aurore",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Richiamo dall\u0027oceano ghiacciato",
        "Client": "Bahari lo scienziato",
        "Description": "Che scocciatura doverlo scrivere\r\ndopo avertelo detto, ma vabb\u00E8...\r\nVoglio che cacci un Somnacanth\r\nfulgido. Io mi occuper\u00F2 della\r\ncattura, tu dovrai proteggermi.\r\nCapito? Bene!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Somnacanth fulgido",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Alles wie immer",
        "Client": "Bahari",
        "Description": "*st\u00F6hn* Als ob ich nicht schon\r\ngenug Papierkram h\u00E4tte! Jetzt\r\nmuss ich auch noch aufschreiben,\r\nwor\u00FCber ich gerade mit dir ge-\r\nsprochen habe... Wie auch immer:\r\nDu jagst das Monster, ich besorge\r\ndie Qurio! Standardprozedur.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Auroracanth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Un ambiente ineficiente",
        "Client": "Bahari, el cient\u00EDfico",
        "Description": "\u00A1Ugh! Como si no tuviera ya\r\nbastante papeleo, ahora tengo\r\nque apuntar lo que te acabo de\r\nexplicar. \u00A1Qu\u00E9 ineficiencia!\r\nEn fin, ya sabes c\u00F3mo va. \u00A1Caza\r\nal monstruo, yo te doy Qurio!",
        "Target": "Caza un Somnacanth Aurora",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
